TITLE: Creating an Interactive Client Component in React
DESCRIPTION: A React client component that maintains state using useState. Marked with 'use client' directive to indicate it should run in the browser and provide interactivity.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/recipes/rsc.md#2025-04-09_snippet_17

