TITLE: Implementing Code Splitting with React.lazy
DESCRIPTION: Example of code splitting implementation using React.lazy for conditional component loading.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/recipes/rsc.md#2025-04-09_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
import { lazy } from "react";

const TextComment = lazy(() => import("./TextComment"));
const ImageComment = lazy(() => import("./ImageComment"));
const VideoComment = lazy(() => import("./VideoComment"));

function Comment({ comment }) {
  switch (comment.type) {
    case "text":
      return <TextComment comment={comment} />;
    case "image":
      return <ImageComment comment={comment} />;
    case "video":
      return <VideoComment comment={comment} />;
  }
}
```

