TITLE: Creating a Basic Optimizer Plugin in JavaScript for Parcel
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates the basic structure of a Parcel Optimizer plugin that transforms bundle contents and source maps. The optimize method receives the bundle contents and source map, performs transformations, and returns the modified versions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/plugin-system/optimizer.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
