TITLE: Environment-Aware Asset Transformation
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to handle different compilation targets based on the environment (browser vs node) when transforming assets.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/plugin-system/transformer.md#2025-04-09_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import {Transformer} from '@parcel/plugin';

export default new Transformer({
  async transform({asset}) {
    let code = await asset.getCode();

    let result = asset.env.isBrowser()
      ? compileForBrowser(code, asset.engines.browser)
      : compileForNode(code, asset.engines.node);

    asset.setCode(result);
    return [asset];
  }
});
```

