TITLE: Build Progress Event Handler
DESCRIPTION: Implementation showing how to handle different phases of the build progress including transforming, resolving, bundling, packaging, and optimizing.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/plugin-system/reporter.md#2025-04-09_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import {Reporter} from '@parcel/plugin';

export default new Reporter({
  report({event}) {
    if (event.type === 'buildProgress') {
      switch (event.phase) {
        case 'transforming':
          process.stdout.write(`Transforming ${event.filePath}...\n`);
          break;
        case 'resolving':
          process.stdout.write(`Resolving ${event.dependency.specifier}...\n`);
          break;
        case 'bundling':
          process.stdout.write('Bundling...\n');
          break;
        case 'packaging':
          process.stdout.write(`Packaging ${event.bundle.displayName}...\n`);
          break;
        case 'optimizing':
          process.stdout.write(`Optimizing ${event.bundle.displayName}...\n`);
         break;
      }
    }
  }
});
```

