TITLE: Adding Dependencies in Parcel Transformer
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to add dependencies to an asset during transformation using the addDependency method.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/plugin-system/transformer.md#2025-04-09_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
import {Transformer} from '@parcel/plugin';

export default new Transformer({
  async transform({asset}) {
    let code = await asset.getCode();
    let deps = code.matchAll(/import "(.*?)"/g);

    for (let dep of deps) {
      asset.addDependency({
        specifier: dep,
        specifierType: 'esm'
      });
    }

    return [asset];
  }
});
```

