TITLE: Creating a Client Component that Uses Server Functions in React
DESCRIPTION: A React client component that calls a server function when clicked. Uses React's startTransition to handle the asynchronous update and useState to manage the like count.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/recipes/rsc.md#2025-04-09_snippet_8

