TITLE: Creating Diagnostic with Code Frames
DESCRIPTION: Example of creating a diagnostic with code frames that include file path, source code, and highlighting specific code regions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/plugin-system/logging.md#2025-04-09_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
throw new ThrowableDiagnostic({
  diagnostic: {
    message: md`Could not parse ${asset.filePath}`,
    codeFrames: [{
      filePath: asset.filePath,
      code: await asset.getCode(),
      codeHighlights: [
        {
          start: {
            line: 1,
            column: 5,
          },
          end: {
            line: 2,
            column: 3,
          },
          message: 'Expected a string but got a number'
        }
      ]
    }]
  }
});
```

