SOURCE: https://github.com/parcel-bundler/website/blob/v2/src/migration/parcel-1.md#2025-04-09_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: bash
CODE:
```
parcel build index.js --target node --bundle-node-modules
```

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "targets": {
    "default": {
      "includeNodeModules": true
    }
  },
  "engines": {
    "node": "10"
  }
}
```

